name: Tim Banks is a melanated Bacchus

content.value:
Last weekend, I won Pan Am championships and didn’t even crack a smile. 

Today, I started crying and had to walk away because I couldn’t get a cake out of pan.

I don’t have anything clever to say, just want y’all to know that anyone can struggle with anything.
